summary: This is an email chain from January 18, 2019, discussing scheduling a meeting to discuss a trip related to Epstein. The participants are coordinating their availability, with one person traveling back and another unaware of any business in Florida the previous day.
keyFacts: Email correspondence dated January 18, 2019, referencing Epstein.
